# Ownership map for the Puzzle Hub monorepo.
#
# Rule of the road: a mechanic folder is PRIVATE to its owner; the SHARED layer
# requires review from the shared-layer steward so a change can't silently break
# another mechanic. Shared code is additive-only for mechanic owners — add
# options/components, don't change existing behaviour. See docs/MECHANIC_SDK.md.

# --- Shared layer: design system, core, composition root, docs ---
/src/app/                @yemelianenko-d
/src/core/               @yemelianenko-d
/src/ui/                 @yemelianenko-d
/src/config/             @yemelianenko-d
/src/platform/           @yemelianenko-d
/src/scenes/             @yemelianenko-d
/public/assets/shared/   @yemelianenko-d
/docs/                   @yemelianenko-d
/ARCHITECTURE.md         @yemelianenko-d
/CLAUDE.md               @yemelianenko-d
/.github/                @yemelianenko-d

# --- Mechanics: each folder owned by its specialist ---
/src/mechanics/sorting/            @yemelianenko-d
/public/assets/mechanics/sorting/  @yemelianenko-d
/src/mechanics/blocks/             @yemelianenko-d
/public/assets/mechanics/blocks/   @yemelianenko-d
